247
00:12:04,820 --> 00:12:05,300
We caught the thief!

248
00:12:05,490 --> 00:12:06,250
We caught the thief!

249
00:12:06,250 --> 00:12:07,540
I'm not a thief! I'm a shopkeeper!

250
00:12:07,580 --> 00:12:08,420
You're the one we're after!

251
00:12:10,010 --> 00:12:11,060
