♪No tea plant is left withered♪

862
00:43:36,560 --> 00:43:44,050
♪The sky drops rain, birds eat worms,
and chickens leave manure♪

863
00:43:44,050 --> 00:43:51,470
♪Using effort and sweat
to water and nourish♪

